# Abstract

This GEP proposes eight enhancements to GASD 1.1 that formalize annotation semantics, introduce contract modeling, and strengthen specification precision — enabling machine-driven static analysis, adversarial testing, and explicit assumption tracking. All changes are fully backward compatible: existing GASD 1.1 files parse and behave identically under GASD 1.1 processing. **New constructs are REQUIRED in GASD 1.2 files.** A file declaring `VERSION 1.2` MUST include these constructs where applicable.

