# Non-Functional Requirements

| Requirement | Target |
| --- | --- |
| Backward compatibility | 100% — all GASD 1.1 files parse identically |
| Specification integrity | Strictly additive — zero deletions or modifications to GASD 1.1 text |
| Grammar completeness | Full EBNF grammar included — every production rule present and verified |
| Determinism | Strict — same input produces same AST and same analysis output |
| Parse performance | < 50ms for files up to 10,000 lines |
| Traceability | Full — every new construct maps to GASD 1.1 spec section |
| Error clarity | All errors and warnings include file location, construct, and actionable guidance |

